edu.stanford.nlp.util

Class GoogleNGramsSQLBacked

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.util.GoogleNGramsSQLBacked

  • public class GoogleNGramsSQLBacked
extends Object
    To query Google Ngrams counts from SQL in a memory efficient manner. To get count of a phrase, use GoogleNGramsSQLBacked.getCount(phrase). Set this class options using Execution.fillOptions(GoogleNGramsSQLBacked.class, props); Created by Sonal Gupta
